Also, it will be a number of concerts by artists representing Latvia throughout the first century, with a focus on the development of music. I would like to take the opportunity again to especially emphasise our immense gratitude and appreciation to the Latvian Community for their contribution to the celebrations during our centenary year," noted the President at the end of the institution’s opening ceremony.

The ministry informs that the contribution made by the Latvian Community to this event in terms of financial contributions and reflections on various projects appears to be overly significant as compared with other communities contributing to celebrations of Latvia’s centenary.

The second day of the festive events in Riga took place on 15 November and was Asta Bertaina day in Latvia.

The Latvian community was reminded of a single voter regarding possible amendments to the Constitution and local election laws. It was agreed that members of the Latvian Community should vote in favour of such amendments.

These actions intend to contribute to the creation of a common message of the Latvian Community: you have the opportunities and wide possibilities in Latvia, the opportunities and the ones you mainly need.
